{"tid":606494,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"講下西營盤","createTime":"2018-03-26T13:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-01T06:16:53.000Z","uid":119825,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b29552e441bd4b6b308a09d585e6f50f1fb8a51f","tid":606494,"uid":119825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:50:04.000Z","msg":"上網睇到好幾個專頁都係講西營盤歷史同保育，係咪西營盤人特別懷舊?<br />\n行過幾次，覺得好舊區feel,但又唔係話好多嘢買，都係食嘢同普通民生嘢多。<br />\n電車路一帶有幾間好似做大陸人生意嘅酒店，但同時區內酒樓又好似出奇地少。<br />\n有冇住嗰度嘅人講下嗰度嘅生活係點，多唔多嘢玩?會唔會想搬走，近幾年係咪多咗大陸人同鬼佬，住西營盤嘅你想未來發展成點?"},{"pid":"0d6f37966c77ce0e86fc98632262345299b25e06","tid":606494,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:51:09.000Z","msg":"住左廿年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n通左地鐵有生氣左好多"},{"pid":"aef2a0b06389f23ee7253f72b30c82e6ac2fbfe4","tid":606494,"uid":24025,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-26T13:53:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d0e400a40bbef38911fb663ea6e333188e836950","tid":606494,"uid":119825,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-27T05:16:50.000Z","msg":"我都覺好似無乜嘢做咁，無商場又無戲院，cafe就一大堆。"},{"pid":"23295bd0b27ce9bef5c30f07e57589369f387b16","tid":606494,"uid":119825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T06:16:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}